<br>
3 kinds of mobs there.  Pull the drakes 1st, then pull the undine spirits (they are hiding in the building, up inside a whole in ceiling, cleric mobs), and then do sphinxs.<br>
<br>
Clearing the drakes will take some doing, plan on dying quite a bit at first.  Once you kill a few and get them spread apart more, it gets easier.  <br>
<br>
The <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>most important </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> thing you must have is a cleric who does NOT HEAL during battles.  If you have a wipe out, you need him to be non-aggro so he can simply drag and rez everyone and start again.<br>
<br>
For example, you go to pull your first drake and you end up with 4.  As long as you kill 1 or 2 of them, you've made progress.  Even if the other ones wipe you out.  The cleric can go check for loot, rez everyone, and rebuff for the another pull.<br>
<br>
The undine spirts are pretty easy, and mezzable.  You will get several at a time when pulled.<br>
<br>
The Sphinx have <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Deathtouch</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  You want to make sure you push them away from each other or they can assist.  They DT at the beginning, so whoever hits it first is dead.  And then every 30 seoncds after that, so you really want to nuke them hard and fast.<br>
<br>
<br>
